org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) AND projects.status IN ('1') ORDER BY projects.lft ASC LIMIT "$1" OFFSET "$2"

rewrites.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13) LIMIT 1) AND projects.status IN ('1') ORDER BY projects.lft ASC LIMIT "$1" OFFSET "$2"
